snippet.description:
We tune in to catch the first ever launch of an orbital satellite from UK soil under Virgin Orbit's "Start Me Up" mission, where we will see the iconic Boeing 747 dubbed "Cosmic Girl" depart Spaceport Cornwall and jettison the rocket "Launcher One" into space.

Special mention to Virgin Orbit for allowing us to broadcast this historic occasion.
